node.text: Our new favorite shade arrives tomorrow 🤎 #comingsoon #vitaminaswim

✨GIVEAWAY✨ We’ve partnered with our friends at @farmacybeauty + @pressedjuicery to give you everything you need for a sunny, nourishing, and skin-safe beach day! We’re giving two lucky winners $600 worth of gift cards to @vitaminaswim @farmacybeauty + @pressedjuicery

How to enter:
1. Follow @farmacybeauty, @vitaminaswim, + @pressedjuicery
2. Like + save this post (on all accounts)!
3. Tag someone below who you want to have a beach day with (each comment = 1 entry)

*Open to U.S. residents only. Must be 18 or older to win. No purchase necessary. Ends on 8/14 at 11:59pm CT. Winners will be selected and contacted from this verified account only via DM. We do not send any registration links from other accounts. This promotion is in no way sponsored by, endorsed by, administered by, or associated with Instagram.
